<h2> Organizer Approval </h2>
<p> SCDT will not run a Process without consent from its Organizer. Subject to the terms of any separate written agreement between SCDT and the Organizer regarding use of the Platform or a Process, SCDT will only support a Process after approving a request from its Organizer that identifies the Organizer and the group of individuals who are potential Process Participants and defines the purpose and timeframe for the Process.
</p>
<h2> Reporting to the Organizer </h2>
<p> The Organizer will be able to observe the responses from Participants and will have access to some identifiable data about Participants that is collected by the Platform or disclosed by a Participant during the Process. Upon request, SCDT will provide the Organizer with de-identified or anonymized data from the Process, without personally identifiable information.
